    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i really don't want to go to the hospital if i don't have to. it's always so stressful and expensive and i've had these exact same feelings during panic attacks before. the heaviness is there but it's not really \"pain,\" it's just... tight? and i'm not even short of breath. do you think it's possible it's just my anxiety acting up again? i have some propranolol here, should i just take one of those to calm down?",
